Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.12,0:03:33.91,yingwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}and will never be apart
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.13,0:03:40.56,yingwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}so we leave for tomorrow
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.76,0:03:47.28,yingwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}to start our lives again
